{"tid":1528881,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[校巴攻略] 唔識車嘅朋友請入","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T16:38:06.000Z","uid":15495,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9674c4d9a4a53f511d1f3049e97cc57e5025500a","tid":1528881,"uid":15495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"之前都有唔少人分享過有「鬼巴士」嘅出現，攪到人心惶惶，而家比個Tips 大家：<br />\n<br />\n認住呢兩個牌子，如果部校巴係呢兩個牌子嘅房車嘅話就加倍警惕：<br />\n<br />\nKIA 起亞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.miamilakesautomall.com/kia-blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/88/2018/12/miami-lakes-automall-kia-motors-logo-1024x512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamilakesautomall.com%2Fkia-blog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F88%2F2018%2F12%2Fmiami-lakes-automall-kia-motors-logo-1024x512.png&h=996b14f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRenault 雷諾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.car-brand-names.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Renault-logo-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.car-brand-names.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FRenault-logo-2.png&h=e67738a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上兩間車廠都有拎咗政府合約。<br />\n<br />\n另外附上校巴驗證Bot 比大家求證: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkaeb_car_plate_check_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkaeb_car_plate_check_bot&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702IR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=10589a6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkaeb_car_plate_check_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果咁多位車台巴打有補充可以留言更新，好人一生平安。"},{"pid":"15d13954be105bc1c2470bd2851f059caf718cfb","tid":1528881,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57